“How strange, how sad! Sad, because I know hardly anything about your life, my darling (moy dushka). The Zemskis were terrible rakes (razvratnikï), one of them loved small girls, and another raffolait d’une de ses juments and had her tied up in a special way—don’t ask me how” (double-hand gesture of horrifled ignorance) “—when he dated her in her stall. Kstati (à propos), I cou